1
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:33,140
[Cage of Shadows]

2
00:01:33,470 --> 00:01:36,120
[Episode 22]

3
00:01:42,580 --> 00:01:43,350
Master.

4
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:45,200
I failed to maintain discipline

5
00:01:45,210 --> 00:01:46,289
and deserve death.

6
00:01:47,810 --> 00:01:49,030
Kill her,

7
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:51,060
and I will absolve you of all guilt

8
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:52,970
and let the matter rest.

9
00:02:03,350 --> 00:02:05,210
Thank you for your mercy, Master.

10
00:02:11,580 --> 00:02:14,410
Zhuang Wujiu, you have rebelled
against your superiors

11
00:02:14,410 --> 00:02:16,560
and shown utter disrespect
for your elders.

12
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,880
Out of our years

13
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:20,150
of father–daughter bond,

14
00:02:20,250 --> 00:02:21,710
I will give you one chance—

15
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:22,800
end your own life.

16
00:02:22,820 --> 00:02:25,020
Spare me the trouble of doing it myself.

17
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,640
So

18
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:05,880
your so-called fatherly affection
was just an act in the end.

19
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:08,080
You couldn't even keep up the pretense.

20
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,480
Preposterous!

21
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:11,700
I gave you life.

22
00:03:12,200 --> 00:03:14,000
If I want you dead, you will die.

23
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,920
My mother gave me my life.

24
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:19,050
Back then, you defiled my mother
in Lingya Tower.

25
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:23,210
Do you know that my very existence
is the shame she carried all her life?

26
00:03:37,290 --> 00:03:39,050
Even if I wronged your mother,

27
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:40,760
I have not treated you badly.

28
00:03:40,990 --> 00:03:42,770
Forcing me back to Lingya Tower back then

29
00:03:42,770 --> 00:03:45,370
was only to turn me
into your killing weapon.

30
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:49,470
You used all those so-called rules
of propriety and family ethics
to control me.

31
00:03:49,470 --> 00:03:51,329
But when life and death were on the line,

32
00:03:51,329 --> 00:03:53,910
I was nothing more than
a disposable pawn to you.

33
00:03:53,910 --> 00:03:55,520
That is your destiny.

34
00:03:56,590 --> 00:03:58,820
And today, I will reclaim your life.

35
00:04:02,730 --> 00:04:04,730
You are not worthy of being a father.

36
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:08,880
Wujiu,

37
00:04:09,740 --> 00:04:10,950
be obedient.

38
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:14,400
Listen to me.

39
00:04:16,529 --> 00:04:17,490
"Be obedient."

40
00:04:17,510 --> 00:04:18,930
"Resign yourself to fate."

41
00:04:18,930 --> 00:04:21,190
I've heard those words countless times.

42
00:04:21,470 --> 00:04:22,410
And every time I hear them,

43
00:04:22,410 --> 00:04:24,340
my urge to kill you grows stronger.

44
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:26,120
You lowly woman!

45
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:28,700
There is no forgiveness for your crimes.

46
00:04:40,950 --> 00:04:42,240
Meng Shuo, your crimes
are beyond redemption.

47
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,330
Heaven cannot tolerate you.

48
00:04:43,330 --> 00:04:44,760
For my mother,

49
00:04:45,320 --> 00:04:48,310
and for all the lives
you trampled in Lingya Tower,

50
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:51,290
I will carry out justice
in the name of heaven.

51
00:04:52,340 --> 00:04:53,060
Wujiu...

52
00:04:53,090 --> 00:04:53,620
do you...

53
00:04:54,210 --> 00:04:57,050
do you truly hate me that much?

54
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,130
If not for Yanzhi,

55
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:25,600
why would I have needed
to wait until today?

56
00:05:34,340 --> 00:05:35,470
What a performance.

57
00:05:36,310 --> 00:05:37,700
This is the most brilliant

58
00:05:37,700 --> 00:05:39,950
death match

59
00:05:40,570 --> 00:05:41,810
I've ever seen.

60
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,560
What a pity—

61
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:46,520
Meng Shuo labored for Lingya Tower
for so many years,

62
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:49,700
only to end up dying at the hands
of his own daughter.

63
00:05:50,570 --> 00:05:52,980
Tragic... truly tragic.

64
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:55,460
No need for this hypocritical sympathy.

65
00:05:55,970 --> 00:05:56,730
You are

66
00:05:57,159 --> 00:05:59,880
the true culprit
behind Lingya Tower's crimes.

67
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:07,200
Just them?

68
00:06:07,510 --> 00:06:09,230
You think they can stop me?

69
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,400
Hahaha...

70
00:06:11,470 --> 00:06:14,030
Young people are always so impatient.

71
00:06:14,410 --> 00:06:16,010
The show isn't even over yet—

72
00:06:16,050 --> 00:06:18,650
why rush to leave the stage?

73
00:06:25,020 --> 00:06:26,200
Qi.

74
00:06:26,990 --> 00:06:27,770
Yanzhi.

75
00:06:30,970 --> 00:06:31,930
Let her go.

76
00:06:32,100 --> 00:06:33,110
Zhuang Wujiu,

77
00:06:34,159 --> 00:06:36,720
I'll make you finish this performance.

78
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:38,950
Surrender yourself...

79
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:39,920
or

80
00:06:42,030 --> 00:06:43,590
watch her die.

81
00:06:58,080 --> 00:06:58,920
You...

82
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,940
You are truly despicable.

83
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:04,960
Hahahahaha...

84
00:07:17,610 --> 00:07:19,540
As a senior statesman of the realm,

85
00:07:19,670 --> 00:07:21,780
you privately established Lingya Tower

86
00:07:21,780 --> 00:07:24,000
and even took pleasure
in enslaving people.

87
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:26,380
Aren't you afraid
that one day the truth will come out

88
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:27,420
and you'll be utterly disgraced

89
00:07:27,420 --> 00:07:29,120
and infamous for all eternity?

90
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,480
Do you really think

91
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:32,990
exposing my identity

92
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,590
will bring down Lingya Tower?

93
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,600
Hmph.

94
00:07:38,150 --> 00:07:39,090
How childish.

95
00:07:40,340 --> 00:07:41,760
Over the years,

96
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:44,680
it's not that no one has known
who I truly am—

97
00:07:45,440 --> 00:07:47,300
they simply don't dare speak out.

98
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:50,270
Because they all understand

99
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:51,860
that the moment

100
00:07:51,980 --> 00:07:53,840
anyone tries to reveal the truth,

101
00:07:54,700 --> 00:07:56,380
I won't even need to give an order—

102
00:07:56,380 --> 00:07:58,980
someone will make sure they stay silent.

103
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:01,420
You are utterly inhuman,

104
00:08:01,450 --> 00:08:03,380
completely devoid of conscience.

105
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,440
You will face retribution.

106
00:08:06,270 --> 00:08:07,070
Retribution?

107
00:08:09,060 --> 00:08:11,060
You mean these death row prisoners?

108
00:08:11,290 --> 00:08:13,410
If you think they were forced into it,

109
00:08:14,470 --> 00:08:16,040
you're mistaken.

110
00:08:17,810 --> 00:08:19,010
You don't believe me?

111
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:20,400
Fine.

112
00:08:20,490 --> 00:08:22,400
Then I'll let you see it clearly.

113
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:25,970
Qi,

114
00:08:26,930 --> 00:08:29,060
open every cell door.

115
00:08:31,570 --> 00:08:33,210
Open all the cells.

116
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:45,730
These low-born criminals
are guilty of grave offenses.

117
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:49,560
Even if they escape, so what?

118
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,640
They'll still have nowhere to belong,

119
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:55,040
nowhere to live in the light of day.

120
00:08:55,040 --> 00:08:56,680
At least here,

121
00:08:56,850 --> 00:08:58,640
they can cling
to what little life they have left

122
00:08:58,640 --> 00:09:00,640
and live out the rest of it in misery.

123
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:03,680
Hahahaha...

124
00:09:06,450 --> 00:09:09,650
Hahahaha...

125
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:14,480
Hahahaha...

126
00:09:19,650 --> 00:09:20,650
Qi,

127
00:09:21,010 --> 00:09:22,560
you've done well this time.

128
00:09:22,870 --> 00:09:26,600
It wasn't a waste keeping you
in hiding in the Tower all these years.

129
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:28,840
You are truly a visionary, Master.

130
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,900
I have only been acting under orders.

131
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:34,670
Qi,

132
00:09:35,160 --> 00:09:36,290
from this moment on,

133
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:39,020
you are the new Tower Master
of Lingya Tower.

134
00:09:40,850 --> 00:09:42,910
I am honored by your support, Master.

135
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:46,280
I will serve you
even at the cost of my life.

136
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:03,880
Qi...

137
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:05,080
You're awake?

138
00:10:07,500 --> 00:10:09,460
If a new bride sleeps this much,

139
00:10:09,540 --> 00:10:11,720
she'll surely be picked on
by her in-laws one day.

140
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:13,520
Hahaha...

141
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:14,880
Thankfully,

142
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:17,160
they're already dead.

143
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:26,160
What did you make me eat?

144
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:27,040
Relax.

145
00:10:28,560 --> 00:10:30,890
It's just some tendon-weakening powder.

146
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,240
How could I ever hurt you?

147
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:39,600
I finally found you after all this time—

148
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,920
I won't lose you again.

149
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:43,960
You're holding me too tightly...

150
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:44,680
It hurts.

151
00:10:45,560 --> 00:10:47,360
Can you help me up?

152
00:10:47,380 --> 00:10:48,180
I'm sorry.

153
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:50,170
I didn't mean to.

154
00:11:03,670 --> 00:11:05,670
I have no idea how Master is doing...

155
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:08,440
For now, I can only pretend to comply.

156
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,120
Yanzhi,

157
00:11:12,580 --> 00:11:15,220
can you pat my head again?

158
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:17,640
Just like before.

159
00:11:33,150 --> 00:11:33,950
Qi,

160
00:11:36,250 --> 00:11:39,670
did you choose that name yourself?

161
00:11:39,690 --> 00:11:40,610
No.

162
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:45,080
They gave it to me.

163
00:11:45,420 --> 00:11:47,290
I hate being called that,

164
00:11:48,580 --> 00:11:50,360
so I killed everyone

165
00:11:51,930 --> 00:11:53,210
who called me that.

166
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:57,210
Everyone—except Master, of course.

167
00:11:57,210 --> 00:11:58,550
But

168
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:01,800
I call you that too.

169
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:05,220
You're different.

170
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,790
I like you.

171
00:12:07,710 --> 00:12:09,390
I like it when you call me that.

172
00:12:09,410 --> 00:12:10,330
Qi,

173
00:12:11,860 --> 00:12:13,630
you said "Master" just now.

174
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:16,540
Are you with Meng Shuo?

175
00:12:16,540 --> 00:12:19,600
Hahaha...

176
00:12:21,970 --> 00:12:23,410
Thanks to your master,

177
00:12:23,860 --> 00:12:25,190
Meng Shuo is dead.

178
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,440
Now

179
00:12:27,940 --> 00:12:30,000
I am the Tower Master of Lingya Tower.

180
00:12:30,920 --> 00:12:31,720
You...

181
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:35,420
How could you be the Tower Master?

182
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:38,050
Then... where is my master?

183
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:40,770
I've served Master for many years.

184
00:12:41,060 --> 00:12:43,320
Of course this is Master's arrangement.

185
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:45,740
Your master tried to assassinate Master

186
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:47,720
and was captured.

187
00:12:49,150 --> 00:12:52,420
The "Master" you refer to is Hei Ya.

188
00:12:54,520 --> 00:12:55,850
Then where is my master?

189
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,840
If you want her to live,

190
00:12:59,250 --> 00:13:00,570
you'll do as I say.

191
00:13:12,100 --> 00:13:13,270
Qi...

192
00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:16,440
you've set this place up like this...

193
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:17,660
are you—

194
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:20,640
I want to marry you.

195
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:22,180
Tomorrow night

196
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:25,080
will be our wedding night.

197
00:13:25,830 --> 00:13:28,610
You want to marry me?

198
00:13:28,920 --> 00:13:29,840
Don't worry.

199
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:32,080
I won't hurt you.

200
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:34,800
I'm now the Tower Master
of Lingya Tower.

201
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:36,780
I can give you whatever you want.

202
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:42,240
I just want you by my side

203
00:13:44,280 --> 00:13:45,720
and to treat you well.

204
00:13:47,280 --> 00:13:48,260
Qi...

205
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:49,600
I...

206
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:51,220
getting married like this

207
00:13:51,280 --> 00:13:52,830
is all too sudden.

208
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:54,460
I... I-I...

209
00:13:54,640 --> 00:13:56,880
I know you like me,

210
00:13:56,880 --> 00:13:57,760
Qi.

211
00:13:58,200 --> 00:14:01,380
But feelings take time to grow.

212
00:14:02,380 --> 00:14:05,580
Why don't we spend
a few more days together?

213
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:08,240
Let me calm my heart first.

214
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,360
Okay?

215
00:14:09,620 --> 00:14:10,860
Nan Yanzhi,

216
00:14:12,160 --> 00:14:13,960
we're both intelligent people.

217
00:14:14,780 --> 00:14:17,140
There's no need for such lies.

218
00:14:17,520 --> 00:14:18,520
Qi,

219
00:14:20,330 --> 00:14:21,970
if you truly care for me,

220
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:23,600
you should respect me

221
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:24,840
and not force me.

222
00:14:24,860 --> 00:14:25,950
Nan Yanzhi,

223
00:14:26,760 --> 00:14:28,280
do you know how much effort I spent

224
00:14:28,280 --> 00:14:30,940
persuading Master to allow this wedding?

225
00:14:33,090 --> 00:14:33,950
Tomorrow night

226
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:36,600
is the Lantern Festival—

227
00:14:37,360 --> 00:14:39,130
and the time of our wedding.

228
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:40,650
If you agree to marry me,

229
00:14:41,520 --> 00:14:42,680
your master

230
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,520
and all your friends

231
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:47,790
will be alive to attend our wedding.

232
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,200
If you refuse,

233
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:53,130
then there won't be any wedding...

234
00:14:57,040 --> 00:15:00,270
and there's no reason
for them to live either.

235
00:15:01,810 --> 00:15:02,530
Alright.

236
00:15:03,140 --> 00:15:04,000
I'll marry you.

237
00:15:04,280 --> 00:15:05,920
Hahaha...

238
00:15:06,560 --> 00:15:08,520
But I have one condition:

239
00:15:09,430 --> 00:15:11,560
not a single one of them
can be missing.

240
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:28,160
So you're one of Hei Ya's people.

241
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:31,800
If not for that,

242
00:15:33,160 --> 00:15:36,090
perhaps we would never
have had such a relationship.

243
00:15:37,400 --> 00:15:38,600
"The relationship?"

244
00:15:39,160 --> 00:15:40,160
You and I walk different paths.

245
00:15:40,160 --> 00:15:41,680
There is no relationship between us.

246
00:15:41,680 --> 00:15:43,880
You are Yanzhi's master.

247
00:15:44,880 --> 00:15:46,140
I've come to invite you

248
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:49,240
to witness our wedding.

249
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:51,960
Release Yanzhi. Now.

250
00:15:53,520 --> 00:15:54,520
Don't worry.

251
00:15:55,800 --> 00:15:58,060
I am now the Tower Master
of Lingya Tower.

252
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:01,720
Yanzhi will be safe—

253
00:16:02,390 --> 00:16:03,960
as long as she marries me.

254
00:16:04,520 --> 00:16:05,440
Hmph.

255
00:16:05,760 --> 00:16:07,360
You? You're not even worthy.

256
00:16:08,270 --> 00:16:10,800
Look at yourself in the water
and see who you are.

257
00:16:10,800 --> 00:16:11,760
How are you

258
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:13,520
any different from Meng Shuo?

259
00:16:13,520 --> 00:16:15,050
I am nothing like Meng Shuo.

260
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,380
He was driven by greed.

261
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:20,210
I have only Yanzhi in my eyes.

262
00:16:21,860 --> 00:16:23,700
You are beyond saving.

263
00:16:35,400 --> 00:16:37,460
Truthfully... I sometimes envy you.

264
00:16:38,740 --> 00:16:41,520
You got to stay by Yanzhi's side
and share so much with her.

265
00:16:41,520 --> 00:16:44,180
Thank you for taking care
of her all these years.

266
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:47,520
From here on,

267
00:16:49,040 --> 00:16:50,600
I will take care of her.

268
00:17:00,380 --> 00:17:02,620
Dao. Chilantuya.

269
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:10,480
You two,

270
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:13,260
please come in.

271
00:17:19,380 --> 00:17:20,770
It's you.

